Package data.regex.definitions

Class Regex

java.lang.Object
data.regex.definitions.Regex
Direct Known Subclasses:
AlternationRegex, ConcatenationRegex, EmptySetRegex, EmptyWordRegex, KleeneStarRegex, SymbolRegex
public abstract class Regex extends Object
An abstract class for a regular expression that only allows alternation ("+"), concatenation and kleene star ("*") operations. The empty set "{}" and the empty word "_" are also valid elementary regular expressions. It also allows brackets "(", ")". Each inheriting regular Expression must return a string representation and an associated alphabet. This class also provides several calculation methods.
